other_tests.findings: Hepatic parenchyma within normal limits; hemangioma in segment 2 measuring 3.0 x 1.9 x 2.6 cm; small stones in the gallbladder (up to 11 mm) without evidence of wall edema or impacted stones; unremarkable pancreas; normal echogenicity of the spleen; no hydronephrosis in kidneys.
